who wish to join a team of technology enthusiasts and work together on interesting projects. We offer flexible working hours, a benefits package, the opportunity for development within two career paths – technical and business-analytical, as well as team-building trips and an atmosphere of mutual respect.</p> Senior Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central Consultant <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>attractive remuneration on a B2B basis</li>\n<li>possibility to use paid time off</li>\n<li>work on projects \"from A to Z\"</li>\n<li>Polish and international projects</li>\n<li>co-financing for trainings and courses</li>\n<li>work in an office in Warsaw or hybrid work</li>\n<li>co-financing for Multisport card</li>\n<li>relaxation zone, chess, billiards, board games, PlayStation, as well as team outings and integration trips</li>\n<li>long-term cooperation (not looking for someone short-term).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>co-creating and developing the BC team</li>\n<li>developing and deepening knowledge of oneself and other team members</li>\n<li>analyzing customer requirements in selected areas of the company</li>\n<li>modeling business processes</li>\n<li>configuring systems according to customer requirements</li>\n<li>designing and testing solutions based on business requirements and expectations,</li>\n<li>consulting on functionalities with IT teams (Managers, Developers).</li>\n<li>creating and maintaining technical documentation</li>\n<li>participating in Dynamics 365 Business Central/NAV system implementation projects</li>\n<li>supporting customers in data migration to the system</li>\n<li>actively participating in project meetings</li>\n<li>training users in selected areas</li>\n<li>supporting users in the initial system operation period</li>\n<li>building good and lasting relationships with customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>minimum 5 years of experience in implementing Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central (NAV) systems, experience working with more than one module</li>\n<li>extensive knowledge of ERP systems operation</li>\n<li>familiarity with relational databases and SQL language (at least at a basic level)</li>\n<li>experience in functional consulting, business analysis, documentation creation, and reporting</li>\n<li>experience in user training and system testing</li>\n<li>ability to collaborate with business, understand business needs, and translate them into IT solutions</li>\n<li>analytical thinking skills</li>\n<li>ability to work according to established schedules and budgets</li>\n<li>ability to build long-term relationships with clients</li>\n<li>you have a high personal culture</li>\n<li>knowledge of English language at a minimum level of B2</li>\n<li>ability to work in agile methodologies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Additional advantages:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>experience in team building and management</li></ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(297,6813,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Job description<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p>Our client is a renowned IT company that has been delivering innovative Microsoft technology-based solutions for over 15 years. As a Microsoft Gold Partner, it specializes in services related to Microsoft Dynamics 365, SharePoint, Office 365, Power BI, and Azure, offering comprehensive business support from custom application development to CRM and cloud solution implementations. Thanks to long-term partnerships with clients both domestically and internationally, the company has earned a reputation as a provider of the highest quality solutions, valuing professionalism and a personalized approach. We are currently looking for ambitious IT specialists, programmers, developers, and consultants who wish to join a team of technology enthusiasts and work together on interesting projects. We offer flexible working hours, a benefits package, the opportunity for development within two career paths – technical and business-analytical, as well as team-building trips and an atmosphere of mutual respect.</p> Senior Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central Consultant <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>attractive remuneration on a B2B basis</li>\n<li>possibility to use paid time off</li>\n<li>work on projects \"from A to Z\"</li>\n<li>Polish and international projects</li>\n<li>co-financing for trainings and courses</li>\n<li>work in an office in Warsaw or hybrid work</li>\n<li>co-financing for Multisport card</li>\n<li>relaxation zone, chess, billiards, board games, PlayStation, as well as team outings and integration trips</li>\n<li>long-term cooperation (not looking for someone short-term).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>co-creating and developing the BC team</li>\n<li>developing and deepening knowledge of oneself and other team members</li>\n<li>analyzing customer requirements in selected areas of the company</li>\n<li>modeling business processes</li>\n<li>configuring systems according to customer requirements</li>\n<li>designing and testing solutions based on business requirements and expectations,</li>\n<li>consulting on functionalities with IT teams (Managers, Developers).</li>\n<li>creating and maintaining technical documentation</li>\n<li>participating in Dynamics 365 Business Central/NAV system implementation projects</li>\n<li>supporting customers in data migration to the system</li>\n<li>actively participating in project meetings</li>\n<li>training users in selected areas</li>\n<li>supporting users in the initial system operation period</li>\n<li>building good and lasting relationships with customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>minimum 5 years of experience in implementing Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central (NAV) systems, experience working with more than one module</li>\n<li>extensive knowledge of ERP systems operation</li>\n<li>familiarity with relational databases and SQL language (at least at a basic level)</li>\n<li>experience in functional consulting, business analysis, documentation creation, and reporting</li>\n<li>experience in user training and system testing</li>\n<li>ability to collaborate with business, understand business needs, and translate them into IT solutions</li>\n<li>analytical thinking skills</li>\n<li>ability to work according to established schedules and budgets</li>\n<li>ability to build long-term relationships with clients</li>\n<li>you have a high personal culture</li>\n<li>knowledge of English language at a minimum level of B2</li>\n<li>ability to work in agile methodologies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Additional advantages:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>experience in team building and management</li></ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(298,6814,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Opis stanowiska<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p