 users to maximize work efficiency. Gaining the trust of over 18,000 teams worldwide, our client is constantly looking for talents ready to join their dynamically growing community. We are seeking individuals from various fields, such as programming, sales, project management, or marketing, who want to co-create the future of work time management. Join us and help shape the future of efficient teamwork, taking advantage of the opportunity to integrate with over 100 applications. This position offers not only the possibility of professional development but also the chance to impact the productivity and success of organizations around the globe.</p> React Developer with knowledge of C++ <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Attractive salary</li>\n<li>Remote work possibility</li>\n<li>Medical package, sports package, training budget</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Developing and maintaining desktop applications in Electron with React/C++.</li>\n<li>Additionally, includes the development of native C++ applications using wxWidgets.</li>\n<li>Integrating applications with external systems.</li>\n<li>Collaborating with a team using Agile/Scrum methodologies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum 3-4 years of experience in creating React applications</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Electron API (IPC, native modules, security)</li>\n<li>Minimum 1-2 years of experience in C++ programming</li>\n<li>Familiarity with C++ standards</li>\n<li>Ability and willingness to program with AI support</li>\n<li>Knowledge of cross-platform development</li>\n<li>Proficient in English - communicative level</li>\n<li>Proficient in Polish - fluent level</li>\n<li>Ability to work in a team</li>\n<li>Independence and proactivity</li>\n<li>Willingness for continuous development and learning of new technologies</li>\n<li>Analytical thinking and problem-solving</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Additional advantages:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Experience with wxWidgets/QT library is a big plus</li></ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(301,6817,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Job description<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p>Our client is an innovative technology company that has been revolutionizing time management for years, offering advanced tools for productivity monitoring, project management, invoicing, and profitability analysis. With flexible pricing plans that cater to the needs of various organizations - from startups to large enterprises, our client enables its users to maximize work efficiency. Gaining the trust of over 18,000 teams worldwide, our client is constantly looking for talents ready to join their dynamically growing community. We are seeking individuals from various fields, such as programming, sales, project management, or marketing, who want to co-create the future of work time management. Join us and help shape the future of efficient teamwork, taking advantage of the opportunity to integrate with over 100 applications. This position offers not only the possibility of professional development but also the chance to impact the productivity and success of organizations around the globe.</p> React Developer with knowledge of C++ <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Attractive salary</li>\n<li>Remote work possibility</li>\n<li>Medical package, sports package, training budget</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<