udgets</li>\n<li>ability to build long-term relationships with clients</li>\n<li>you have a high personal culture</li>\n<li>knowledge of English language at a minimum level of B2</li>\n<li>ability to work in agile methodologies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Additional advantages:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>experience in team building and management</li></ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(488,7004,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Job description<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p>Our client is a renowned IT company that has been delivering innovative Microsoft technology-based solutions for over 15 years. As a Microsoft Gold Partner, it specializes in services related to Microsoft Dynamics 365, SharePoint, Office 365, Power BI, and Azure, offering comprehensive business support from custom application development to CRM and cloud solution implementations. Thanks to long-term partnerships with clients both domestically and internationally, the company has earned a reputation as a provider of the highest quality solutions, valuing professionalism and a personalized approach. We are currently looking for ambitious IT specialists, programmers, developers, and consultants who wish to join a team of technology enthusiasts and work together on interesting projects. We offer flexible working hours, a benefits package, the opportunity for development within two career paths – technical and business-analytical, as well as team-building trips and an