rket leader in IT, the company continuously invests in technology development and expands its offer with new, innovative products and services. Due to dynamic growth, we are looking for ambitious employees who will join our team of professionals. We offer the opportunity to work in a stable and constantly developing company that values creativity, innovation, and commitment.</p> Developer Microsoft Dynamics 365 Finance &amp; Operations (D365 F&amp;O) <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Attractive salary</li>\n<li>Medical package and sports card</li>\n<li>Participation in a prestigious enterprise-class ERP system implementation project</li>\n<li>Opportunity to work in a dynamic and innovative environment</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours and possibility of remote work in bigger part</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Development and evolution of applications and functionalities in the Microsoft Dynamics 365 F&amp;O system.</li>\n<li>Design and implementation of system integrations using Azure Service Bus (ASB).</li>\n<li>Analysis and resolution of system operation-related issues.</li>\n<li>Collaboration with functional consultant teams and business analysts.</li>\n<li>Participation in implementation projects, including testing and technical documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum 2-3 years of experience working as a Microsoft Dynamics 365 F&amp;O developer.</li>\n<li>Practical knowledge of the accounting module in D365 F&amp;O.</li>\n<li>Experience in designing and implementing integrations with Azure Service Bus (ASB).</li>\n<li>Good understanding of programming languages X++, C#, and SQL Server technologies.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with the Visual Studio development environment.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of CI/CD procedures.</li>\n<li>Analytical thinking and problem-solving skills.</li>\n<li>Ability to work in a team and good communication.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Additional advantages:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of Azure DevOps environment.</li>\n<li>Experience working in Agile methodologies.</li>\n<li>Microsoft Dynamics certifications.</li>\n</ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(594,7110,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Job description<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p>Our client is an innovative technology company that has specialized in cloud computing solutions since 2025, focusing on the AWS platform. With extensive experience in designing, building, deploying, and maintaining IT environments and applications, both in the cloud and on-premises, the company is recognized as a leader in cloud migration, data processing, artificial intelligence, DevOps, cloud optimization, cybersecurity, and cloud application development. The team consists of certified experts and partners with competencies in key technological areas, enabling the provision of services at the highest level. The company collaborates with clients from various industries, helping them to maximize the potential of cloud technologies for their business. We are currently looking for talented specialists with experience in cloud technologies who want to join our team and support us in delivering innovative solutions.</p> Senior Cloud Engineer - AWS <p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Training budget and sponsored AWS certifications</li>\n<li>Paid time off, private medical care, Multisport card</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours, remote work</li>\n<li>Free English lessons</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Designing and implementing AWS architectures (*EC2, EKS, Lambda, RDS, S3, IAM, VPC, API Gateway, CloudWatch, Route 53*)</li>\n<li>Creating infrastructure as code (*Terraform, AWS CDK*)</li>\n<li>Building and maintaining CI/CD (*GitHub Actions, GitLab Pipelines, Jenkins, AWS CodePipeline*)</li>\n<li>Scripting and automation using *Python, TypeScript, Go, Bash*</li>\n<li>Container management (*Docker, Kubernetes, Amazon ECS/EKS*)</li>\n<li>Ensuring security (IAM policies, encryption, compliance, HA architectures)</li>\n<li>Monitoring and observability (*CloudWatch, Prometheus, Grafana, ELK/EFK*)</li>\n<li>Technical support, consulting, and knowledge sharing with the team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum 4-5 years of experience in Cloud/DevOps/SRE role</li>\n<li>Proficiency in AWS services and IaC tools</li>\n<li>Experience in CI/CD, containerization, and automation</li>\n<li>Knowledge of security practices and network design</li>\n<li>Very good command of Polish and English language</li>\n<li>AWS certifications</li>\n</ul></div></section>','',NULL,NULL),(595,7111,'<h3 class=\"text-c20\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full text-left flex items-center\" id=\"1-header\" aria-controls=\"1-panel\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Opis stanowiska<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"20\" class=\"ml-auto\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.47 7.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06L12 9.31l-6.97 6.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></button></h3><section id=\"1-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"1-header\" class=\"font-normal\"><div class=\"content list--check mt-6 -mb-6\"><p>Nasz klient to renomowana firma z branży IT, która od ponad 15 lat dostarcza innowacyjne rozwiązania informatyczne oparte na technologiach 