unities for growth.</li>\n<li>Social impact – contribute to products that make digital life easier for businesses and communities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Our Streamlined Hiring Process</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Intro call with one of our team members.</li>\n<li>Portfolio review and design interview with PM + CTO.</li>\n<li>Welcome aboard! ?</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>? Ready to launch the next-gen of SaaS products with us? Apply now and let’s build something extraordinary.</strong></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>3+ years of experience as a UI/UX Designer, with&nbsp;<strong>commercial SaaS products</strong>.</li>\n<li>Proven track record designing&nbsp;<strong>complex dashboards, workflows, or B2B SaaS interfaces</strong>.</li>\n<li>Strong skills in&nbsp;<strong>Figma</strong>&nbsp;(design systems, prototyping).</li>\n<li>Understanding of&nbsp;<strong>UX research methods</strong>&nbsp;and ability to apply insights.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with&nbsp;<strong>designing for event-driven or data-heavy products</strong>&nbsp;(analytics, pipelines, dashboards).</li>\n<li>Knowledge of&nbsp;<strong>accessibility standards</strong>&nbsp;and responsive web design.</li>\n<li>Ability to collaborate with engineers, PMs, and non-technical stakeholders.</li>\n<li><strong>Mandatory:</strong>&nbsp;Portfolio with SaaS product case studies (not only marketing websites). Applications without a SaaS-related portfolio will not be considered.</li>\n<li>Fluent in English and Polish.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1258,7774,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"lin