i>\n<li>potrafisz płynnie komunikować się zarówno w mowie jak i w piśmie w języku <strong>angielskim </strong>oraz <strong>polskim</strong>.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1259,7775,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Matrix Eastern Europe, the offshore division of Matrix IT, one of the leading global R&amp;D services companies with more than 11,000 professionals, is looking for Senior BI Developer / Data Solution Architect a to join the team of our client and partner – Stampli!</p>\n<p>Stampli is seeking a talented Senior BI Developer / Data Architect to join our growing Data &amp; Analytics team. As a Data Architect, you will play a major role in scaling our existing BI Platform, Data Warehouse (DWH), and Data Management operations. You will be responsible for building unique ETL processes that transform raw data into valuable business insights.</p>\n<p>The role is ideal for candidates who are adept at balancing hands-on development work and project management/system design responsibilities.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Minimum 5 years of experience in developing BI systems, including at least 3 years of experience in ETL development and strong SQL capabilities.</li>\n<li>Experience in BI development using Qlik and leading BI projects independently.</li>\n<li>Experience in business, economic, or marketing analysis.</li>\n<li>Practical experience in the field of Data Warehouses (DWH) using ETL tools.</li>\n<li>Practical experience with AWS RedShift, Matillion for ELT/ETL processes, and/or AutoML processes + developments is a big plus.</li>\n<li>Strong Excel skills.</li>\n<li>Great team player with excellent communication skills and the ability to collaborate with multidisciplinary teams within the company.</li>\n<li>Ability to take ownership of end-to-end solution creation, including design, development, user interface, usage, and analytics.</li>\n<li>A self-starter and agile learner who thrives in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1260,7776,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Zostań&nbsp;<strong>SAS Developerem</strong>&nbsp;i pracuj na projekcie dla naszego klienta - to jedna z największych i najbardziej rozpoznawalnych instytucji finansowych w Europie, oferująca nowoczesne rozwiązania w zakresie ubezpieczeń, inwestycji i zarządzania ryzykiem. Organizacja stawia na stabilność, długofalowy rozwój oraz kulturę współpracy opartą na zaufaniu i innowacyjności. Praca w tym środowisku to szansa na udział w strategicznych projektach o dużej skali i znaczeniu biznesowym.</p>\n<h3>Oferujemy</h3>\n<p><strong>Stawka:</strong>&nbsp;do&nbsp;<strong>180 PLN netto + VAT / h (B2B)</strong><br><strong>Tryb pracy:</strong>&nbsp;hybrydowy –&nbsp;<strong>1 dzień w tygodniu w biurze w Warszawie</strong><br><strong>Godziny pracy:</strong> pon.–pt. 8:00–16:00 lub 9:00–17:00</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Wykształcenie wyższe kierunkowe (informatyka, elektronika, telekomunikacja lub pokrewne).</li>\n<li>Minimum&nbsp;<strong>4 lata doświadczenia</strong>&nbsp;w roli&nbsp;<strong>SAS Developera</strong>.</li>\n<li>Bardzo dobra znajomość:&nbsp;<strong>SAS 9.4M6</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>SAS Base</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>SAS DI</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>SAS Enterprise Guide</strong>.</li>\n<li>Dobra znajomość&nbsp;<strong>baz danych relacyjnych</strong>, szczególnie&nbsp;<strong>Oracle</strong>.</li>\n<li>Umiejętność&nbsp;<strong>projektowania procesów ETL</strong>.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w&nbsp;<strong>generowaniu i analizie raportów</strong>&nbsp;oraz&nbsp;<strong>analizie kodu</strong>.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w&nbsp;<strong>migracji SAS</strong>&nbsp;(do innej wersji lub systemu).</li>\n<li>Zaangażowanie, proaktywność i umiejętność pracy zespołowej.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1261,7777,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>? <strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Kraków/Warsaw (Hybrid)<br>?&nbsp;<strong>Contract type:</strong>&nbsp;B2B only<br>?&nbsp;<strong>Industry:</strong>&nbsp;Banking / KYC / Client Onboarding</p>\n<p>We are currently looking for an experienced&nbsp;<strong>Machine Learning Developer</strong>&nbsp;to join a strategic global banking initiative within the Onboarding and Know Your Customer (OBKYC) stream. This area is key to enabling seamless onboarding and client verification for a wide range of clients – from sole traders to international corporations.</p>\n<p>You’ll join a cross-functional, global team of engineers, data scientists, and product managers working to drive the adoption of&nbsp;<strong>AI/ML solutions for document classification, data extraction and Generative AI-based automation.</strong></p>\n<ul></ul>\n<p><strong>What we offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Opportunity to work on global AI transformation projects in one of the world’s leading financial institutions.</li>\n<li>High-impact work on real business challenges – your models will go into production.</li>\n<li>Access to a modern ML tech stack and supportive expert teams.</li>\n<li><strong>Hybrid working model</strong>&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>B2B contract only</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>? Interested?</p>\n<p>Let’s talk! Apply now or reach out directly to learn more about the team, project and technical challenges we’re solving.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Hands-on experience in&nbsp;<strong>Document AI / Intelligent Document Processing</strong>&nbsp;using traditional models and Generative AI.</li>\n<li>Strong Python programming skills and experience with&nbsp;<strong>ML, DL, NLP, OCR</strong>.</li>\n<li>Proficiency with frameworks such as&nbsp;<strong>PyTorch, TensorFlow, HuggingFace, Spacy, OpenCV, Regex</strong>, or similar.</li>\n<li>Awareness of&nbsp;<strong>secure coding</strong>, resilience and deployment best practices for production environments.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1262,7778,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Creating an inspiring place to thrive for the talented, we use their expertise and courage to introduce the technology of the future into your business. - This is the foundation of&nbsp;<strong>Mindbox</strong>&nbsp;and the goal of our business and technology journey. We operate and develop in four areas:</p>\n<p><strong>?</strong><strong>&nbsp;Autonomous Enterprise</strong>&nbsp;- automation of business processes using RPA, OCR, and AI.</p>\n<p><strong>?</strong><strong>Business Managment Systems ERP</strong>&nbsp;- we implement, adapt, optimize, and maintain flexible, safe, and open ERP of production and distribution companies worldwide.</p>\n<p><strong>?</strong><strong>Talent Network</strong>&nbsp;- we provide access to the best specialists.</p>\n<p><strong>☁️</strong><strong>&nbsp;Modern Architecture</strong>&nbsp;- we build integrated, sustainable, and open CI / CD environments based on containers enabling safe and more frequent delivery of proven changes in the application code.</p>\n<p>We treat technology as a tool to achieve a goal. Thanks to our consultants\' reliability and proactive approach, initial projects usually become long-term cooperation. For over 16 years, it has provided various services to support clients in digital transformation.</p>\n<p>#LI-Hybrid&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>We offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>We are open to the employment form according to your preferences</li>\n<li>Work with experienced and engaged team, willing to learn, share knowledge and open for growth and new ideas</li>\n<li><strong>Hybrid working system (6x per month from the office in Kraków)</strong></li>\n<li>Mindbox is a dynamically growing IT company, but still not a large one – everybody can have a real impact on where we are going next</li>\n<li>We invest in developing skills and abilities of our employees</li>\n<li>We have attractive benefits and provide all the tools required for work f.e. computer</li>\n<li>Interpolska Health Care, Multisport, Warta Insurance, training platform (Sages)</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Experience of data engineering, ETL processes</li>\n<li>At least 7 years of professional experience in SQL development</li>\n<li>Experience in GCP, Big Query</li>\n<li>Experience with data build tools (DBT)</li>\n<li>Experience with Airflow, Cloud Composer</li>\n<li>Experience of data modelling</li>\n<li>Experience with data streaming, e.g. Kafka</li>\n<li>Experience with BI tools – mainly Looker Studio</li>\n<li>Experience making trade-offs when designing schemas and marts</li>\n<li>Experience with implementing automated data quality solutions</li>\n<li>Experience in orchestration and scheduling</li>\n<li>Experience working in a DevOps environment, i.e. think, build, and run</li>\n<li>Experience with Continuous Integration, Continuous Delivery</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1263,7779,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Dla naszego klienta, globalnej firmy zajmującej się outsourcingiem procesów biznesowych (BPO) i usługami analitycznymi, która wspiera organizacje w optymalizacji operacji, wykorzystaniu danych i transformacji cyfrowej, szukamy doświadczonej osoby, która wesprze nasz zespół w obszarze analityki danych i planowania inwestycji marketingowych. Na tym stanowisku będziesz odpowiadać za modelowanie finansowe (ENSUM+), analizy efektywności inwestycji, konsolidację wiedzy z rynków oraz wspieranie decyzji biznesowych poprzez zaawansowane analizy danych.</p>\n<p><strong>Nasz klient oferuje:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pracę w międzynarodowym środowisku z dużą ekspozycją biznesową.</li>\n<li>Możliwość rozwoju w obszarze zaawansowanej analityki i modeli predykcyjnych.</li>\n<li>Pracę zdalną na terenie całej Polski</li>\n<li>Podstawa + bonus uzależniony od indywidualnych wyników</li>\n<li>Ofertę benefitów do wyboru: prywatna opieka medyczna w LuxMed, karta multisport, bilety do kina, vouchery na zakupy</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Doświadczenie w modelowaniu finansowym i symulacjach inwestycyjnych.</li>\n<li>Bardzo dobra znajomość marketing mix modelling (MMM) i analityki danych.</li>\n<li>Umiejętność pracy z SQL, Pythonem i Power BI.</li>\n<li>Znajomość systemów danych korporacyjnych i chmurowych platform analitycznych.</li>\n<li>Umiejętność przekładania danych na praktyczne wnioski biznesowe.</li>\n<li>Doskonałe zdolności komunikacyjne i współpracy z interesariuszami.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1264,7780,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>AI Engineer / Python developer +&nbsp; AWS + LLM Agents</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote-first&nbsp;<br><strong>Employment type:</strong> B2B Contract</p>\n<p>? <strong>Role Overview</strong></p>\n<p>We’re looking for an <strong>AI Engineer</strong> to design, implement, and maintain <strong>agentic AI systems</strong> for our clients. You’ll work across <strong>LLMs, orchestration frameworks, and data pipelines</strong> to deliver <strong>robust, observable, and secure automations</strong>.</p>\n<p>This is <strong>not a research-only role</strong> — every project you take on will target <strong>production environments and real business use cases</strong>, with measurable impact. You’ll join a hands-on team that thrives on solving complex problems, shipping production-grade systems, and pushing the boundaries of what AI can do in real-world settings.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>1–2+ years of hands-on experience building <strong>LLM-powered agents</strong> or complex automations</li>\n<li>Strong <strong>Python</strong> skills (async programming, testing, packaging)</li>\n<li><strong>TypeScript</strong> experience is a plus (it’s an emerging language in our stack)</li>\n<li>Practical experience with <strong>LangGraph / LangChain</strong> and one or more of: <strong>n8n, AWS Bedrock, Airflow, Prefect, Temporal</strong></li>\n<li>Working knowledge of <strong>Gemini, OpenAI, and Claude ecosystems</strong> (prompting, function calling, structured output)</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of <strong>vector stores, embeddings, RAG patterns, and data quality</strong></li>\n<li>Strong software engineering foundations: <strong>Git, code reviews, CI/CD, containerization, cloud (AWS preferred)</strong></li>\n<li>Familiarity with <strong>ADK (Agent Development Kit)</strong> or similar frameworks</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1265,7781,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Wspólnie z naszym partnerem&nbsp;<strong>irlandzką firmą technologiczną rozwijającą nowoczesną platformę do zarządzania zapasami w sektorze gastronomicznym,</strong>&nbsp;poszukujemy doświadczonej osoby na stanowisko&nbsp;<strong>Android Developer.&nbsp;</strong>Będziesz odpowiedzialny(a) za rozwój, wdrażanie nowych funkcji oraz integrację z usługami backendowymi.</p>\n<p><strong>✨ OFERUJEMY:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Uczestnictwo w spotkaniach integracyjnych oraz meetupach technologicznych, umożliwiających dzielenie się wiedzą i doświadczeniem.</li>\n<li>Rozwój kariery i długofalową współpracę w firmie o ugruntowanej pozycji na rynku.</li>\n<li><strong>Realny wpływ na projekt</strong>&nbsp;– Twoje pomysły i inicjatywy będą mile widziane!</li>\n<li>5000 PLN za polecenie znajomego do naszych projektów.</li>\n<li>Dostęp do najnowszych technologii i narzędzi pracy.</li>\n<li><strong>Możliwość pracy 100% zdalnej</strong></li>\n<li>Szybki i zdalny proces.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Dziękujemy za wszystkie zgłoszenia. Pragniemy poinformować, że skontaktujemy się z wybranymi osobami.</em></p>\n<h3><em>12408/MG</em></h3></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Dobrej znajomości&nbsp;<strong>komponentów architektury Androida</strong>&nbsp;i najlepszych praktyk projektowych oraz&nbsp;<strong>Biegłej znajomości Kotlin.</strong></li>\n<li>Wiedzy z zakresu&nbsp;<strong>architektury offline-first</strong>&nbsp;i lokalnego przechowywania danych.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenia z&nbsp;<strong>Jetpack Compose</strong>&nbsp;lub nowoczesnymi frameworkami UI.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenia z&nbsp;<strong>RESTful API</strong>&nbsp;i programowaniem&nbsp;<strong>asynchronicznym.</strong></li>\n<li>Swobody w pracy z&nbsp;<strong>Git</strong>&nbsp;i zespołowym workflow.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1266,7782,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><ul>\n<li>The possibility to work on a unique product with international outreach.<br></li>\n<li>One week per quarter we all work from the office.</li>\n<li>General onboarding program and Fudo Buddy who will help you in your first steps.</li>\n<li>Possibility to work with professionals with wide experience from which you can learn.</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours.</li>\n<li>Spacious and modern office with access to free drinks and snacks.</li>\n<li>Your personal MacBook.</li>\n<li>Benefits such as medical care (Medicover), sport card (Multisport Plus), group life insurance (Unum), cafeteria system (Worksmile).</li>\n<li>Cooperation in the form of B2B contract.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Fudo Security is a leader in the IT security industry creating products for secure remote access. We pride ourselves in our passionate people, and our professional space. We work together every day to deliver value and quality to our customers. Passion, enthusiasm and achieving results is part of our work culture. &nbsp;We have offices in two locations: one in Silicon Valley and second in Warsaw. Fudo has hundreds of clients in 30 &nbsp;countries all over the world. For sure you know most of our clients, as they are the biggest and well-known companies on Polish and international markets. We are the first Polish company which was listed in the Gartner’s Magic Quadrant for the PAM industry! We’ve been appreciated many times and have received many awards - e.g. Cybersecurity Excellence Awards, InfoSec Awards and others. We are always focused on the quality of our product and ensuring it meets the security needs of our clients. As a #cybersecurity company we’re #constantly setting trends on the market. We introduce new products to the market and focus on growth. Staying safe in the cyber world with #FudoSquad is a very rewarding and challenging experience! &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our DNA - passion, proactivity, ownership, loyalty, honesty &amp; fairness, teamwork, persistence.</p>\n<p>We don\'t want the above to be just slogans. We strive to ensure that these values guide us every day and are visible in our actions. We believe deeply that bringing together a diversity of thoughts, perspectives, and expression is key for building the best-in-class product. To achieve this, we need to constantly work towards making Fudo Security the best place to work, for everyone. We want each of our employees to be an essential part of our #FudoSquad!</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>proficiency in Python programming (5 years of experience),</li>\n<li>practical knowledge of building regression and classification models,</li>\n<li>good knowledge about neural networks, decision trees, forests etc.,</li>\n<li>being familiar with techniques like deep learning, transfer learning,</li>\n<li>proficiency in ml frameworks like scikit-learn, tensorflow,</li>\n<li>good understanding of architectures eg. autoencoder, gann etc.,</li>\n<li>skills in NLP, creating and using transformer models (Attention Is All You Need) will be an asset,</li>\n<li>good command of SQL,</li>\n<li>communication skills, effective self-planning, and proper prioritization of tasks.</li>\n',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `job_details` VALUES (1267,7783,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Are you a passionate backend expert ready to shape the future of high-performing, scalable web applications? We’re looking for a <strong>PHP Backend Technical Leader</strong> to join our growing tech team — someone who thrives on solving complex problems, mentoring others, and driving technical excellence.</p>\n<p>As a key technical leader, you’ll play a central role in designing robust architectures, optimizing backend performance, and guiding your team toward best practices. You’ll collaborate closely with product managers, frontend developers, and DevOps engineers to build modern, reliable solutions that power exceptional user experiences.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>PHP Expertise: Expert knowledge of application development in PHP is required, with a strong focus on modern development practices. Hands-on experience in application development (minimum 5 years in a commercial environment is needed)</li>\n<li>Frameworks: Vast experience with Symfony is a must</li>\n<li>Architecture: Solid understanding of Domain Driven Design (DDD) and hexagonal architecture. Experience with object-oriented programming, design patterns, and multi-layered application structures</li>\n<li>Database Abstraction: Knowledge of Object-Relational Mapping (ORM), specifically Doctrine in Symfony, understanding of DQL (Doctrine Query Language) or similar abstraction layers</li>\n<li>Languages: Polish at native or C2 level and English at C1 level</li>\n<li>Nice to have: Experience in working with AI driven IDEs would be beneficial and a basic familiarity with Docker for local development is beneficial, but not critical as onboarding materials and team support are available</li>\n<li>Nice to have 2: Familiarity with Laravel is a plus</li>\n<li>Nice to have 3: Experience with Jira or similar task management tools is helpful but can be learned quickly</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1268,7784,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>Unisystech Consulting</strong> is a Canadian IT outsourcing company. You will be working on projects for leading Canadian banks and financial institutions.</p>\n<p>Currently we are looking for a Backend Developer with experience in Node.js and AWS&nbsp;to join our team. In this role, you will design, develop, and maintain scalable backend solutions,&nbsp;build APIs, and contribute to the overall solution architecture of our platform.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Contract type:</strong> B2B (no additional benefits, we only pay for the worked hours) or employment contract</p>\n<p><strong>Working hours: </strong>12:00-20:00 (Polish time), work on Canadian calendar</p>\n<p><strong>Location: </strong>100% in the office, Warsaw or Krakow</p>\n<p><strong>Currency</strong>: we pay in CAD or USD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Experience in backend development (4 years+)</li>\n<li>Cloud expertise in <strong>AWS </strong>(Lambda, ECS, API Gateway, DynamoDB, S3, etc.)</li>\n<li>Strong expertise with the <strong>Node.js </strong>framework</li>\n<li>Experience in designing <strong>microservices</strong> and <strong>serverless</strong> architectures</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of <strong>RESTful </strong>and <strong>GraphQL APIs </strong>development</li>\n<li>Familiarity with <strong>CI/CD pipelines, Docker, </strong>and <strong>Kubernetes</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Availability to work afternoon-evening hours (12:00-20:00) and fully in the office&nbsp;</strong></li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1269,7785,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><ul></ul>\n<p><strong>Opis oferty</strong></p>\n<p>Proggramista Java będzie odpowiedzialny za projektowanie i rozwój aplikacji e-commerce B2B we współpracy z zespołami międzyfunkcyjnymi. Obejmuje to zapewnienie skalowalności, bezpieczeństwa i standardów jakości platformy. Programista Java będzie współpracował z innymi programistami back-endowymi i fullstack, aby dostarczać najlepsze w swojej klasie rozwiązania na rynku. Do obowiązków programisty należy również aktywna komunikacja z Właścicielem Platformy i Menedżerem Produktu w celu ustalenia właściwych priorytetów i zrozumienia bieżących potrzeb użytkowników.</p>\n<p><strong>Metodyka:</strong> Agile / Scrum-of-Scrums</p>\n<p><strong>Proces rekrutacji:</strong></p>\n<p>Spotkanie techniczne ( weryfikacja wiedzy)<br>Spotkanie z działem HR i managerem projektu</p>\n<p><br><strong>WAŻNE INFORMACJE:</strong></p>\n<p>W trakcie procesu rekrutacji na kolejnych jej etapach wymagana będzie weryfikacja tożsamości kandydata.<br>Pierwszy dzień pracy odbywać się będzie stacjonarnie w siedzibie Euvic w Gliwicach przy ul. Przewozowa 32.<br></p>\n<p><strong>Euvic - </strong>ponad 5000 pracowników i 20 lat doświadczenia niewątpliwie czynią nas dużą firmą. A jednak, mimo upływu czasu i stale powiększającego się grona klientów wciąż jesteśmy firmą stworzoną przez inżynierów IT dla inżynierów IT. Tworzymy prężnie rozwijającą się firmę „z ludzką twarzą”, składającą się z dobrych ludzi, tworzących dobre oprogramowanie. Czyni nas to solidnym partnerem IT skupiających się na własnych osiągnięciach, sukcesach klientów i satysfakcji zawodowej pracowników.</p>\n<p><strong>Co oferujemy?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>sprawny, szybki i przyjazny proces rekrutacyjny (nie tylko umiejętności są dla nas ważne, wspólnie sprawdźmy, czy pasujesz do the Good People),</li>\n<li>pracę i rozwój w renomowanej firmie IT, z ugruntowaną pozycją na rynku,</li>\n<li>projekty dla klientów międzynarodowych z wielu branż,</li>\n<li>płaską strukturę, politykę „otwartych drzwi” i dbałości o dobre relacje w zespołach,</li>\n<li>małe zespoły w dużej firmie i koleżeńską wspólnotę w tych zespołach,</li>\n<li>transparentny i atrakcyjny program szkoleniowy oparty na badaniach kompetencji,</li>\n<li>bonusowy program poleceń,</li>\n<li>wsparcie buddiego w okresie onboardingu,</li>\n<li>rozwój wewnątrz organizacji – szkolenia wewnętrzne, „Euvic Talks”, możliwość prowadzenia wewnętrznych szkoleń,</li>\n<li>udział w inicjatywach społecznych – wspieramy potrzebujących z udziałem Fundacji The Good People.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>W Euvic tworzymy środowisko pracy oparte na równości, szacunku i otwartości. Wierzymy, że różnorodność talentów i perspektyw napędza innowacje oraz wspiera zrównoważony rozwój. Dlatego nasze procesy rekrutacyjne są projektowane w sposób, który zapewnia każdemu kandydatowi równe szanse, niezależnie od pochodzenia, płci, wieku, orientacji seksualnej, stanu zdrowia czy innych indywidualnych cech. Dążymy do budowania kultury pracy, w której każdy może rozwijać swój potencjał i czuć się w pełni akceptowany.</p>\n<p><strong>Zastanawiasz się czy warto?</strong></p>\n<p>W naszym wewnętrznym badaniu #theGoodPeople wskazali 4 kluczowe aspekty, które cenią najbardziej:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Sam/a decyduję o tym, jak najlepiej wykonać swoją pracę.</li>\n<li>Mój manager/ka jest dostępny, otwarty na sugestie i odmienność zdania.</li>\n<li>Jestem traktowany/a z należytym szacunkiem.</li>\n<li>W moim zespole panuje atmosfera sprzyjająca współpracy.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Brzmi jak dobre miejsce pracy dla Ciebie?</p>\n<p><strong>Wybierz swoje benefity:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>System kafeteryjny (karta Multisport, bilety na wydarzenia sportowe i muzyczne i wiele, wiele więcej),</li>\n<li>Opieka medyczna,</li>\n<li>Ubezpieczenie na życie z możliwością wykupienia dodatkowych pakietów np. opieki onkologicznej,</li>\n<li>Inicjatywy rozwojowe.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Zapraszamy do #theGoodPeople - profesjonaliści, pasjonaci, dobrzy ludzie ?</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Minimum 5 lat doświadczenia</li>\n<li>Dooświadczenie w tworzeniu oprogramowania z wykorzystaniem technologii Java i Spring Boot</li>\n<li>Zrozumienie koncepcji REST API i doświadczenie w jego użytkowaniu i projektowaniu</li>\n<li>Znajomość obsługi zdarzeń (Rabbit/Active MQ lub Kafka)</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w korzystaniu z relacyjnych i nierelacyjnych baz danych (NoSQL)</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie z rozwiązaniami kontenerowymi - obrazy Docker i Kubernetes</li>\n<li>Zainteresowanie umiejętnościami DevOps w chmurze (MS Azure, Terraform), automatyzacja procesów (GitHub actions, Gradle)</li>\n<li>Głębokie zrozumienie aspektów testowania i doświadczenie w automatyzacji testów (testy jednostkowe, integracyjne i E2E)</li>\n<li>Znajomość języka angielskiego (poziom B2 lub wyższy)</li>\n<li>Dobre zrozumienie zasad Agile Software Development (Scrum lub Kanban)</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1270,7786,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Alterdata.io, jako firma usługowa zajmująca się danymi, zatrudni <strong>Senior</strong> <strong>Data Analysta </strong>do pracy zdalnej. Będziesz częścią zespołu profesjonalnych inżynierów, analityków danych i developerów, którzy szukają rozwiązań szytych na miarę.</p>\n<p><br><strong>Co możemy Ci zaoferować:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Swobodne i przyjazne środowisko pracy.</li>\n<li>Pakiet świadczeń dodatkowych (kafeteria, opieka medyczna, multisport).</li>\n<li>Praca w pełni zdalna, ale częste wyjazdy integracyjne.</li>\n<li>Możliwość rozwoju i zdobycia certyfikacji branżowych.</li>\n<li>Pełne wsparcie zespołu i regularne szkolenia wewnetrzne.</li>\n<li>Możliwość szybkiego rozwoju.</li>\n<li>Różne projekty (w tym międzynarodowe).</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Minimum 5 lat doświadczenia komercyjnego na stanowisku Data Analyst.</li>\n<li>Biegłość w SQL - kompleksowe zapytania, optymalizacja, budowa algorytmów analitycznych</li>\n<li>Modelowanie danych.</li>\n<li>Wysoko rozwinięte myślenie biznesowe i umiejętność przekładania celów strategicznych klienta oraz kontekstu biznesowego na konkretne problemy i rozwiązania w obszarze Data Analytics i BI, z udowodnioną zdolnością do dostarczania produkcyjnych rozwiązań generujących wymierną wartość.</li>\n<li>Samodzielność, proaktywność oraz umiejętność rozwiązywania złożonych problemów technicznych.</li>\n<li>Doskonałe umiejętności komunikacyjne i prezentacyjne.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w prowadzeniu projektów, planowaniu prac zespołu oraz w opracowywaniu rozwiązań problemów.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w prowadzeniu zespołu oraz budowaniu zaangażowania i współpracy wśród pracowników.</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w roli lidera technicznego lub koordynatora mniejszych zespołów programistycznych.</li>\n<li>Znajomość narzędzi BI (PowerBi / Tableau / Looker studio).</li>\n<li>Doświadczenie w budowaniu dashboardów z wykorzystaniem projektowania UI/UX.</li>\n<li>Bardzo dobra organizacja pracy, umiejętność pracy w zespole oraz efektywnej komunikacji.</li>\n<li>Skrupulatność i dbanie o szczegóły.</li>\n<li>Znajomość języka angielskiego na poziomie minimum C1.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1271,7787,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>Some careers shine brighter than others.</strong></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a career that will help you stand out, join HSBC, and fulfil your potential. Whether you want a career that could take you to the top, or simply take you in an exciting new direction, HSBC offers opportunities, support and rewards that will take you further.</p>\n<p><strong>Your career opportunity</strong></p>\n<p>Model Risk Management (MRM) at HSBC is structured as a global function, headed up by the Chief Model Risk Officer (CMRO). The MRM function reports directly to the Group Chief Risk and Compliance Officer (GCRCO) ensuring its independence from the model developing and owning areas of the firm.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>MRM are the second line of defence (2LoD) for Model Risk and the CMRO is the global Model Risk Steward for the group and is also accountable for the global operation of the MRM function. MRM teams are based in each region, to ensure local subject matter expertise and to guide, review, and challenge. MRM activity is managed on a global basis as many models are used in multiple locations. This enables MRM to operate consistently and efficiently globally, and to take account of additional local regulatory requirements.</p>\n<p>Independent Model Validation is a specialist quantitative role within the Model Risk Management team responsible for carrying out independent validations of HSBC’s model landscape, in order to identify and communicate model limitations and issues.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Independent Model Validation provides independent challenge of a model’s underlying theoretical assumptions and limitations, its practical implementation, its live application and business usage, providing stakeholders (including model users, senior management, audit and regulators) with assurance that models and tools developed, maintained and used within HSBC Group are fit for their intended purposes and are compliant with applicable internal and supervisory expectations. They will also review remediation plans and activities, undertake portfolio level reviews across model types and challenge the model owners on the appropriate application of relevant policy of models.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Model types include but are not limited to Credit Risk models (Retail and Wholesale), IFRS9 models, Stress Testing and Scenario Analysis models, Economic Capital models, Financial Vulnerability models, Pricing models, Traded Risk models, Insurance Risk models and models covering non-financial areas e.g., transaction monitoring, customer selection and human resources. This includes the traditional model types as well as modern approaches such as machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Master’s or PhD degree in a quantitative discipline like Financial Mathematics, Statistics, Econometrics, Quantitative Finance, Economics or Engineering.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Knowledge in one or more of the following areas: Stress Testing and Scenario Analysis models, Traded Risk and Pricing Models, Global Markets Trading &amp; Hedging models, Asset Liability Models, etc.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Comprehensive knowledge of statistical model and scorecard development techniques.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Risk models, performance metrics and risks and associated issues.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of internal procedures and local regulations and those of other country regulators would be an advantage.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Experience with some statistical modelling software / programming language e.g. SAS, Python, R, Matlab, C++, VBA.</li>\n<li>Experience of developing and reviewing models throughout the customer lifecycle.</li>\n<li>Experience of presenting recommendations to Senior Management.</li>\n<li>Experience of conducting independent model reviews.&nbsp;</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1272,7788,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>Please note - hybrid from Warsaw (3 days from the office, 2 remotely).</strong></p>\n<p><strong>About us:</strong></p>\n<p>We help businesses use AI and digital tools to work better and grow faster, especially in private capital markets. Our Core Platform improves workflows and gives useful insights with AI. Olympus Software is a fast, smart cloud system that grows with your needs. The Pantheon Suite offers flexible tools to manage and improve business performance. With over 10 years of experience, we know how to turn technology into real business value.</p>\n<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p>\n<p>We’re looking for a Quality Assurance Analyst who’s obsessed with getting things right. As part of our PaaS (Platform-as-a-Service) Customer Delivery team in Warsaw, you won’t just test software - you’ll be a key voice in delivering reliable, scalable solutions to our enterprise clients. This is your chance to step into a high-impact role where you’ll help catch issues before users ever see them, drive continuous quality improvement, and act as the final gatekeeper for customer-ready platform features.</p>\n<p>You’ll work closely with engineers, product delivery managers, and business analysts to ensure our releases are rock-solid and our client experiences flawless. If you’re passionate about quality, love to break things (and then figure out why), and want to make your mark in a fast-paced platform environment - we want you on the team.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Design and execute functional, integration, regression, and exploratory test cases.</li>\n<li>Collaborate with engineers and analysts to review requirements and define acceptance criteria.</li>\n<li>Identify, log, and track defects; communicate risks and gaps clearly.</li>\n<li>Maintain test documentation and support UAT with customer delivery teams.</li>\n<li>Support creation and management of automated test suites where applicable.</li>\n<li>Contribute to continuous improvement of QA processes, tooling, and reporting.</li>\n<li>Advocate for quality across all phases of the delivery lifecycle.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Required</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>4+ years of experience in QA or software testing roles.</li>\n<li>Strong understanding of QA methodologies, test planning, and test execution.</li>\n<li>Experience working in Agile environments and with cross-functional teams.</li>\n<li>Comfort using tools like Jira, TestRail, or similar.</li>\n<li>Detail-oriented mindset and ability to think critically about edge cases and failure points.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Preferred</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Familiarity with API testing tools like Postman or Swagger.</li>\n<li>Exposure to test automation frameworks (e.g., Cypress, Selenium, Playwright).</li>\n<li>Understanding of platform-based or multi-tenant application testing.</li>\n<li>Experience with SaaS or configurable enterprise software.</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>4+ years of experience in QA or software testing roles.</li>\n<li>Strong understanding of QA methodologies, test planning, and test execution.</li>\n<li>Experience working in Agile environments and with cross-functional teams.</li>\n<li>Comfort using tools like Jira, TestRail, or similar.</li>\n<li>Detail-oriented mindset and ability to think critically about edge cases and failure points.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1273,7789,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Nasz klient – amerykański FinTech, który od lat łączy świat finansów i zaawansowanych technologii – rozwija w Warszawie swoje drugie europejskie centrum technologiczne. Po sukcesie biura w Londynie, właśnie w Polsce powstaje nowy zespół, który ma stać się centrum globalnych innowacji.</p>\n<p><strong>O projekcie</strong></p>\n<p>Budujemy od zera nowy system post-trade, który będzie integrował dane z wielu systemów tradingowych i kierował je do odpowiednich modułów raportowych, kontrolingowych oraz analitycznych. To kluczowy projekt – fundament przyszłych rozwiązań technologicznych firmy.</p>\n<p><strong>Oferujemy:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wynagrodzenie powyżej 30 000 PLN brutto/miesiąc (UoP + autorskie koszty uzyskania przychodu)</li>\n<li>Pracę w międzynarodowej strukturze o bardzo wysokim poziomie technicznym</li>\n<li>Duży wpływ na kształtowanie architektury i standardów nowego systemu</li>\n<li>Realne możliwości rozwoju</li>\n<li>Hybrydowy model pracy: 3 dni w biurze przy Rondzie Daszyńskiego (Warszawa)</li>\n<li>Środowisko, które wspiera innowacje i daje przestrzeń na technologiczną doskonałość</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Jeśli szukasz miejsca, gdzie Twój kod naprawdę coś zmienia, gdzie od pierwszego dnia tworzysz rozwiązanie od zera i możesz rozwijać się wśród najlepszych – to może być idealny moment, by porozmawiać.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Bardzo dobrze znają Kafka lub C# / .NET, w tym programowanie asynchroniczne i wielowątkowe</li>\n<li>AWS lub Azure&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Mają doświadczenie w pracy z systemami o dużej złożoności i wymaganiach wydajnościowych</li>\n<li>Potrafią analizować dane i projektować stabilne przepływy informacji między systemami</li>\n<li>Są otwarte na współpracę w międzynarodowym środowisku i chcą pracować w kulturze wysokich standardów technicznych</li>\n<li>Cenią rozwój, wiedzę i partnerskie relacje w zespole</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1274,7790,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Nasz klient – amerykański FinTech – w maju 2025 otworzył w Warszawie swoje nowe biuro. To druga europejska lokalizacja po Londynie, która ma stać się strategicznym centrum technologicznym firmy. W planach jest zbudowanie zespołu 200 wysokiej klasy specjalistów, a obecnie w Polsce pracuje już około 80 osób.</p>\n<p>Teraz poszukujemy trzeciej osoby do warszawskiego zespołu DevOps – doświadczonego specjalisty (senior lub dobrego mida), który chce rozwijać się w środowisku o wysokich standardach technicznych i mieć realny wpływ na to, jak powstaje infrastruktura globalnego funduszu inwestycyjnego.</p>\n<p><strong>Oferujemy:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wynagrodzenie powyżej 30 000 PLN brutto/mies. (UoP)</li>\n<li>Udział w budowie i rozwoju globalnego środowiska infrastrukturalnego funduszu</li>\n<li>Duże możliwości rozwoju – praca z nowoczesnym stackiem, wpływ na kierunek rozwoju narzędzi i procesów</li>\n<li>Hybrydowy model pracy: 3 dni w biurze (Rondo Daszyńskiego, Warszawa)</li>\n<li>Pracę w środowisku, które stawia na innowacje, jakość i partnerską współpracę</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To wyjątkowa okazja, by dołączyć do organizacji, która dopiero buduje swoje polskie struktury i daje przestrzeń do rozwoju – technicznego, zawodowego i osobistego. Jeśli chcesz mieć realny wpływ na kształt nowego zespołu i tworzyć rozwiązania klasy enterprise, porozmawiajmy.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Mają doświadczenie w pracy z chmurą publiczną, automatyzacją infrastruktury i konteneryzacją</li>\n<li>Potrafią myśleć systemowo i szukają sposobów na ciągłe ulepszanie środowiska pracy</li>\n<li>Chcą uczestniczyć w budowie nowego centrum technologicznego od podstaw</li>\n<li>Cenią możliwość rozwoju w kulturze technicznej opartej na otwartości i współpracy</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1275,7791,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Nasz klient – <strong>amerykański FinTech</strong> – w zeszłym roku otworzył w Warszawie swoje nowe biuro. To druga po Londynie europejska lokalizacja, która ma stać się kluczowym centrum technologicznym firmy. Docelowo w Polsce powstanie oddział liczący 200 wysokiej klasy specjalistów, a obecnie w zespole pracuje już około 80 osób.</p>\n<p>Prowadzimy rekrutację do zespołu budującego i rozwijającego nowe aplikacje dla obszaru Treasury – systemów wspierających zarządzanie środkami finansowymi firmy, optymalizację warunków pożyczek oraz analizę przepływów pieniężnych. To środowisko, które szybko się rozwija i daje ogromną przestrzeń do nauki, eksperymentowania i wdrażania własnych pomysłów.</p>\n<p><strong>O projekcie</strong></p>\n<p>Zespół rozwija nowoczesne aplikacje dla dwóch kluczowych produktów Treasury (i kolejnych w planach), współpracując bezpośrednio z działami biznesowymi i zespołami quantów, którzy tworzą modele matematyczne wykorzystywane w logice systemów.</p>\n<p>Nie wymagamy wcześniejszej znajomości branży finansowej – ta rola to świetna okazja, by poznać świat finansów od środka, w pracy z globalnym zespołem i realnym wpływem na działanie funduszu.</p>\n<p>Obecnie globalny dział liczy 10 osób, w tym czterech inżynierów i tech lead w Warszawie. Zespół poszerzamy o dwóch kolejnych doświadczonych developerów (senior lub mocny mid).</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Bardzo dobrze znają Python (minimum mid/senior level)</li>\n<li>Potrafią pracować z bazami danych SQL i NoSQL</li>\n<li>Rozumieją architekturę systemów rozproszonych i przetwarzanie danych</li>\n<li>Są otwarte na naukę nowych obszarów i współpracę z biznesem</li>\n<li>Chcą realnie rozwijać się technicznie i domenowo, w środowisku o wysokich standardach inżynierskich</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1276,7792,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Take charge of fulfilling client expectations by managing the planning, execution, and delivery of tailored IT solutions. This includes areas such as infrastructure management, cloud services, system migrations, operational transitions, software tool rollouts, and cybersecurity measures, all aligned with pre-approved service demands. The IT Project Manager will oversee the comprehensive project lifecycle, including strategic planning, resource allocation, financial oversight, timeline management, and team coordination within the delivery framework.</p>\n<p></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>At least 3 years of experience in E2E IT Project management.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>You’re passionate about leading IT initiatives that leverage cutting-edge technologies, with the support of experienced architects to help you bring them to life.</li>\n<li>You’re a people person, recognizing that effective communication is one of the strongest tools a Project Manager can possess—and you’ve mastered it.</li>\n<li>Strong leadership abilities and hands-on experience, not only in overseeing your own tasks but also in managing the activities and performance of your team.</li>\n<li>You can navigate the classic Agile vs. Waterfall debate, adapting methodologies to suit project requirements and client needs, ensuring optimal outcomes for all parties involved.</li>\n<li>You’re fluent in both English and German, and you feel confident engaging with stakeholders at every organizational level.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1277,7793,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>The&nbsp;Experience Management Service Architect&nbsp;is tasked with ensuring the effective establishment of the Experience Management Office (XMO). In this position, you will design the overarching architecture of the experience management ecosystem, ensuring smooth coordination of all technical elements, tools, and platforms necessary for monitoring and improving employee experiences. Collaborating closely with stakeholders, you will align the technical framework with the company’s strategic objectives, guaranteeing that all systems are compatible, scalable, and secure.</p>\n<p></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>At least 4 years of experience in Data Analysis (ETL processes/pipelines, data models..)</li>\n<li>Proficiency in programming languages&nbsp;such as C#, SQL, and frameworks like Entity Framework.</li>\n<li>Strong expertise in developing and managing ELT pipelines&nbsp;using tools like Azure Data Factory or comparable technologies.</li>\n<li>Advanced skills in building sophisticated data models, especially in scenarios where data originates from multiple systems with varying formats. Hands-on experience with tools like SQL Server, Oracle, or data warehousing platforms such as Snowflake or Amazon Redshift is crucial.</li>\n<li>Competence in scripting languages, including Python and PowerShell, to streamline integration workflows and data transformation processes.</li>\n<li>Proven ability to design and deploy RESTful and SOAP APIs, enabling efficient data exchange between systems.</li>\n<li>Strong collaboration skills, with the ability to work closely with multidisciplinary teams, including IT, data engineering, and business stakeholders, while translating complex technical concepts into clear, non-technical language.</li>\n<li>Fluency in both spoken and written English and German, ensuring effective communication at all organizational levels.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1278,7794,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><h3>About the Role</h3>\n<p>We are seeking a seasoned Senior DevOps Engineer to support the reliability, automation, and continuous improvement of our infrastructure and operational processes. The person in this role will work closely with engineering and quality teams to ensure smooth delivery pipelines and stable, secure production environments.<br></p>\n<h3>What We Offer</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Employment contract or B2B collaboration model.</li>\n<li>Hybrid work arrangement (2 days onsite, 3 days remote each week).</li>\n<li>Access to a flexible benefits platform with a variety of programs (sports, travel, culture, recreation, and more).</li>\n<li>Multisport or equivalent sports membership.</li>\n<li>Private healthcare coverage for you and your family.</li>\n<li>Additional life insurance.</li>\n<li>Access to extensive learning and development resources.</li>\n<li>Discounts for cultural events such as theatre performances.</li>\n<li>A diverse and international working environment.</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>At least 6 years of experience in system administration, IT operations, or DevOps engineering.</li>\n<li>Strong practical knowledge of Linux/Unix and Windows server environments.</li>\n<li>Hands-on experience with major cloud service providers such as AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud.</li>\n<li>Proficiency in scripting (e.g., Bash, PowerShell, Python).</li>\n<li>Familiarity with infrastructure-as-code technologies such as Terraform, Ansible, or Puppet.</li>\n<li>Experience working with monitoring and observability tools (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana, Nagios).</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of networking fundamentals, firewalls, and security best practices.</li>\n<li>Strong communication and analytical problem-solving abilities.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1279,7795,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>We are looking for an experienced Engineering Lead with a .NET background to support the development of modern technology solutions within a growing product and engineering organization.</p>\n<p>The local R&amp;D department includes several dozen specialists — developers, test engineers, team leads, and project roles — working on internally built systems as well as solutions delivered in cooperation with external technology partners. The team oversees architectural consistency, systems integration, SDLC standards, and the evolution of shared services used across the organization.</p>\n<p>This position combines responsibilities typical for both an Engineering Lead and a Team Lead, involving the establishment of technical standards as well as hands-on involvement in designing and delivering software solutions.</p>\n<p></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Higher education in Computer Science or another relevant technical field is preferred.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1280,7796,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><h3>About the Role</h3>\n<p>We are looking for a Voice and Collaboration Engineer with strong DevOps and SRE capabilities to join a globally distributed technology team. This role is ideal for someone with solid analytical thinking, deep technical expertise, and excellent communication skills. You will work across enterprise voice, collaboration, automation, and reliability engineering domains.</p>\n<h3>What We Offer</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Collaboration based on a B2B contract.</li>\n<li>Daily use of modern technologies and opportunities to work with international teams.</li>\n<li>Option to work fully remotely (but if you\'re from Warsaw it would be good if you could come to the office once a week).</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or a related discipline, plus 5+ years of relevant industry experience.</li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of enterprise communication platforms, including APIs for cloud collaboration tools and SBC technologies.</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of telecommunication standards, signaling protocols, and voice-routing principles.</li>\n<li>Hands-on experience automating operational workflows using Ansible, Python, and REST APIs.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with core networking, databases, cloud services, and data center operations.</li>\n<li>Experience working with Linux and/or Windows systems; proficiency in scripting or programming.</li>\n<li>Understanding of relational and NoSQL databases.</li>\n<li>Ability to perform root cause analysis, propose temporary workarounds, and drive long-term fixes.</li>\n<li>Strong organizational skills with the ability to work independently and prioritize effectively.</li>\n<li>Experience in the financial sector is advantageous.</li>\n<li>Ability to multitask in a fast-paced environment without compromising quality.</li>\n<li>Comfortable working within both Agile and Waterfall delivery frameworks.</li>\n<li>Passion for modern DevOps practices and cutting-edge automation technologies.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1281,7797,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>An international organization operating within the financial technology and trading industry is looking for a Data Platform Engineer to strengthen its technical team. The company leverages advanced analytics, large-scale data, and modern infrastructure to support systematic trading and research activities across global markets. Collaboration between engineers and researchers is central to its culture, which emphasizes innovation, technical excellence, and continuous improvement.</p>\n<p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p>\n<p>You will be part of a team responsible for the systems that enable data-driven trading strategies. The position focuses on developing and maintaining tools and infrastructure used for large-scale data processing, monitoring, and system automation. The role involves close cooperation with research and engineering teams to ensure stable, high-performance, and low-latency operations.<br></p>\n<p><strong>What’s Offered</strong></p>\n<p>You’ll join a team that values technical depth, collaboration, and innovation. The company encourages open communication, respect, and diversity of perspectives. Alongside professional growth opportunities, employees benefit from initiatives supporting a balanced and healthy work life.<br></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Strong programming experience in Python and good command of shell scripting</li>\n<li>Solid grasp of data engineering principles, including ETL pipelines and time-series data manipulation</li>\n<li>Proficiency in Linux-based systems, with knowledge of networking and system performance analysis</li>\n<li>Experience with containerized and orchestrated environments (e.g., Docker, Kubernetes)</li>\n<li>Familiarity with CI/CD pipelines and infrastructure-as-code practices</li>\n<li>Understanding of monitoring and metrics systems (such as Grafana, Prometheus, or ELK stack)</li>\n<li>Motivation to build scalable, high-performance systems supporting research and trading applications</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1282,7798,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><h3>AWS Cloud Engineer / Architect</h3>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Gdańsk (<strong>on-site</strong>)</p>\n<p><strong>Working hours:</strong> European time zone</p>\n<p><strong>Experience:</strong> 4+ years</p>\n<p><strong>Role overview:</strong></p>\n<p>Responsible for designing, implementing, and maintaining AWS-based cloud solutions within large-scale migration and modernization initiatives. The role involves transitioning systems from on-premise to AWS, supporting infrastructure migration and driving architectural modernization with a strong focus on security, automation, and data ecosystem integration.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>At least 4 years of hands-on experience as an AWS Engineer or Architect.</li>\n<li>Strong, practical knowledge of AWS services, cloud networking, identity and access management, and account operations.</li>\n<li>Experience with Infrastructure as Code tools (Terraform or CloudFormation).</li>\n<li>Excellent command of spoken and written English (technical communication, reporting, and documentation).</li>\n<li>Availability to work on-site in Gdańsk during European business hours.</li>\n<li>Readiness to undergo a background check as part of the onboarding process.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1283,7799,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><h3>AWS Data Engineer / Architect</h3>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Gdańsk (<strong>on-site</strong>)</p>\n<p><strong>Working hours:</strong> European time zone</p>\n<p><strong>Experience:</strong> 4+ years</p>\n<p><strong>Role overview:</strong></p>\n<p>Data expert responsible for designing, building, and maintaining modern Data Lake and Data Warehouse solutions within the AWS cloud environment.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Minimum 4 years of experience as a <strong>Data Engineer</strong> or <strong>Data Architect </strong>within AWS environments.</li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of AWS data services (<strong>Redshift</strong>, S3, Glue, Athena, Lake Formation, Data Pipeline, EMR).</li>\n<li>Proficiency in Python, SQL, or PySpark for data transformation and analytics.</li>\n<li>Proven experience in data migration and modernization projects.</li>\n<li>Excellent command of English for reporting, documentation, and meetings.</li>\n<li>Willingness to work on-site in Gdańsk during European hours.</li>\n<li>Background check may be required before employment start.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1284,7800,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>Some careers shine brighter than others.</strong></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a career that will help you stand out, join HSBC, and fulfil your potential. Whether you want a career that could take you to the top, or simply take you in an exciting new direction, HSBC offers opportunities, support and rewards that will take you further.</p>\n<p><strong>Your career opportunity</strong></p>\n<p>Global Defense Engineering is responsible for fielding solutions that help defend HSBC against a wide range of threats to the business as well as its customers, clients, partners, and staff.&nbsp; The team works in concert, with partner teams across HSBC, to implement novel defensive capabilities that are effective and adaptable against a constantly evolving threat landscape.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The function operates under the vision: “Enabling HSBC to be safely successful everywhere the Firm chooses to do business.”</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Experience working with and securing DDI products in large environments</li>\n<li>Experience working with and securing resilient network layer encryption services</li>\n<li>Experience working with and securing network management products and solutions&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>A background in information systems, technology, architecture, design, and service delivery of defense-in-depth capabilities.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Understanding and knowledge of common industry cyber security frameworks, standards and methodologies</li>\n<li>Experience working within integrated networked on-prem and Cloud environments with Third party and SaaS connectivity and that require cloud use-cases for web/mobile and enterprise companies.</li>\n<li>Experienced in supporting a network capability, technology or platform.</li>\n<li>Extensive knowledge of core networking concepts</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1285,7801,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>We are&nbsp;monday.com, a global software company transforming how businesses run. Our product suite can adapt to the needs of diverse industries and use cases within one powerful platform, empowering ~250,000 customers worldwide to reimagine how work gets done, drive greater efficiency, and scale like never before.</p>\n<p>With over 2,900 employees across the globe, we grow by prioritizing transparency and knowledge sharing. We care about the impact you make, not the hours you clock, so we encourage initiative, ownership, and fresh thinking. We back our people with flexible work, wellness and mental health support, and a work environment built on collaboration.</p>\n<p>We’re looking for an MLOps Engineer to build the infrastructure that keeps our ML models production-grade, cost-efficient, and reliable at scale. You’ll work on everything from observability and pipelines to disaster recovery, ensuring that our AI investments are always serving customers in real time.</p>\n<p>We fully embrace the AI revolution and equip you with AI-powered IDEs, customizable agent rules, prompt engineering tools, and AI-infused CI/CD pipelines designed to boost speed and reliability. You\'ll also tap into AI-driven insights, helping you make smarter decisions, faster.</p>\n<p>The role is based in our Warsaw office - established in 2022, it is a growing hub for engineers who love solving impactful problems. Teams here work on a broad range of challenges that push the boundaries of our products and infrastructure.</p>\n<p><strong>Salary &amp; Compensation</strong></p>\n<p>At&nbsp;monday.com, our total compensation package includes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Base salary</li>\n<li>Bonus target</li>\n<li>Restricted Stock Units (RSUs)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The final offer will depend on the candidate’s experience, skills, and job-related expertise.<strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>From Monday to Wednesday,&nbsp;we\'ll&nbsp;fuel your day with free breakfast and lunch in the office.</li>\n<li>Enjoy private medical care and Multisport card to keep you healthy.</li>\n<li>We\'ve got you covered with life insurance.</li>\n<li>We care of employee\'s mental health as well - you will get access to Calm Mindfulness App.</li>\n<li>Get awesome discounts on our partners\' products and services.</li>\n<li>Join in on our fun team events and get-togethers.</li>\n<li>Look forward to a little something special from us during your birthday and work anniversaries.</li>\n<li>For Online Learning opportunities, you will gain access to LinkedIn Learning.</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>5+ years of experience as an&nbsp;<strong>ML/AI Engineer,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>MLOps, Infrastructure Engineer, or DevOps with ML focus</strong>.</li>\n<li>Proven experience deploying and maintaining&nbsp;<strong>machine learning models in production at scale</strong>.</li>\n<li>Hands-on expertise in&nbsp;<strong>hosting, deploying, and managing&nbsp;</strong>the&nbsp;<strong>infrastructure</strong>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<strong>ML models,</strong>&nbsp;ensuring they are&nbsp;<strong>production-grade, scalable, and reliable.</strong></li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of&nbsp;<strong>CI/CD pipelines, observability, testing, and rollback strategies</strong>.</li>\n<li>Hands-on expertise with&nbsp;<strong>cloud infrastructure (AWS preferred)</strong>, GPUs, and containerized services.</li>\n<li>Experience with&nbsp;<strong>cost monitoring and optimization</strong>&nbsp;for large-scale ML systems.</li>\n<li>Comfort working with&nbsp;<strong>data scientists and ML engineers</strong>, translating research into robust services.</li>\n<li>Bonus: Experience with&nbsp;<strong>fine-tuning models, managing training data, and balancing performance vs. cost trade-offs</strong>.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1286,7802,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Beekeeper and LumApps merged to create the first AI-powered Employee Hub, an all-in-one platform designed to connect and empower every employee - whether desk-based or frontline. LumApps, a SaaS platform dedicated to Employee Experience, helps companies drive digital transformation in communication, collaboration, and engagement with their clients, partners, and, most importantly, their employees. Together, our mission is to redefine the employee experience by integrating communication, productivity, and engagement tools into a unified, intelligent platform that serves over 7 million users globally.</p>\n<p>As a Senior AI Engineer, you will play a pivotal role in our mission by designing, building, and deploying cutting-edge AI solutions for our customers. This high-impact role gives you the ability to shape how AI is used and perceived across an entire industry. You will catapult your career with opportunities to showcase your work alongside industry leaders, as we recently did with&nbsp;AWS.</p>\n<p>You will collaborate closely with one of our dedicated product squads to design, implement, and deploy AI solutions for our customers. Working alongside our talented technical and product teams, you will have ample opportunities to grow your career.</p>\n<p><strong>Our tech stack:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI: We make use of the best of Google Vertex AI technologies, we build agents with AWS Strands</li>\n<li>Cloud Infrastructure as Code: We operate on GCP and AWS across multiple regions and we manage our infrastructure using Spacelift and Terraform.</li>\n<li>Container Orchestration: Our services run in containers using Kubernetes (EKS and GKE) managed with Helm and FluxCD/ArgoCD.</li>\n<li>Backend Services: Predominantly built in Python.</li>\n<li>Data Stores: We utilize PostgreSQL, MySQL, ClickHouse, BigQuery, Redis, and Elasticsearch.</li>\n<li>Monitoring and Logging: Implemented through Prometheus, Datadog, Grafana</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What we offer</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive salary</li>\n<li>Phone &amp; Home Internet costs reimbursement up to 80 PLN/month</li>\n<li>Private health care package with Luxmed – covered for you and partially for your partner / family</li>\n<li>Cafeteria benefits – monthly budget to cover sport cards or other purchases</li>\n<li>Creative Allowance – paid as 1000 PLN gross/month</li>\n<li>Home office set-up reimbursement up to 1000 PLN</li>\n<li>Personal Learning &amp; Development Budget of 1500 USD/year<br></li>\n<li>26 days of annual leave/year</li>\n<li>2 Mental Health days off per year</li>\n<li>Laptop for work purposes</li>\n<li>Hybrid working model<br></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Benefits listed above are part of the compensation package for a contract of employment.&nbsp;</em></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Proven experience as a Software Engineer with 5+ years in backend development</li>\n<li>Strong programming skills in Python</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of Generative AI and Deep Learning models (classification, regression, clustering)</li>\n<li>Solid understanding of machine learning frameworks and libraries (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch, scikit-learn)</li>\n<li>Proven ability to rapidly prototype and iterate on deploying Generative AI solutions</li>\n<li>Knowledge and Experience in techniques to deliver high quality output from Large Language Models</li>\n<li>A high degree of pragmatism, focus on shipping fast and able to adapt to changing business needs that go hand in hand with the speed of innovation in AI</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1287,7803,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>Some careers shine brighter than others.</strong></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a career that will help you stand out, join HSBC, and fulfil your potential. Whether you want a career that could take you to the top, or simply take you in an exciting new direction, HSBC offers opportunities, support and rewards that will take you further.</p>\n<p><strong>Your career opportunity</strong></p>\n<p>The Risk &amp; Control Specialist will be accountable and responsible to deliver activities as defined by the CTO Enablement Risk &amp; Controls Lead (in line with Agile principles, ownerships within the team are expected to change to allow for a different focus; these changes would be discussed and agreed with the role holder with sufficient time for transition).</p>\n<p>The role is performed with a focus on excellence &amp; attention to detail with an ability to lead &amp; inspire other staff, but also to communicate effectively with all levels of technology &amp; business management.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>General knowledge with relevant experience (minimum 5+ years) within Risk Management, Controls Governance &amp; Monitoring or IT Service Continuity Management.</li>\n<li>Strong understanding of regulatory requirements and risk governance practices.</li>\n<li>Good knowledge on Data Security Control or other relevant controls as operated by CTO/Cyber and with knowledge on Information Security Risk Management processes would be advantageous.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of HSBC’s Risk Management Platform (e.g. Helios) would be advantageous but not essential</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Agile Scrum &amp; Kanban as well as familiar with Agile tooling (e.g. Confluence and JIRA) would be advantageous but not essential</li>\n<li>Good knowledge of data analysis/reporting through data visualization/BI tools like PowerBI/Qliksense would be advantageous</li>\n<li>Experience working on complex projects across multiple domains. Ability to interpret complex data and add value to the business decision making process.</li>\n<li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills with a proven ability to communicate effectively and confidently at all levels across the Group and across different cultures.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1288,7804,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>Dla jednego z naszych klientów szukamy:</p>\n<p><strong>IT Murex Consultant&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Model współpracy:&nbsp;100% zdalnie&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Finanse:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>B2B</strong>&nbsp;via 1dea outsourcing, stawka ustalana indywidualnie</p>\n<p><strong>Prosimy o anglojęzyczne CV.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Podsumowanie</strong></p>\n<p>Poszukujemy doświadczonego&nbsp;<strong>Konsultanta IT Murex</strong>, który dołączy do projektu realizowanego dla naszego klienta z sektora finansowego. Projekt dotyczy wdrożenia i rozwoju modułów&nbsp;<strong>Murex MX Test, Back Office, Reporting</strong>&nbsp;oraz rozbudowy narzędzia&nbsp;<strong>Onyx (Murex automated non-regression tool)</strong>.<br>Praca w 100% zdalna, w międzynarodowym środowisku i w długofalowej współpracy.</p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Minimum&nbsp;<strong>10 lat doświadczenia</strong>&nbsp;w pracy z systemem&nbsp;<strong>Murex</strong>&nbsp;(bank lub instytucja finansowa).</li>\n<li>Minimum&nbsp;<strong>4 lata doświadczenia</strong>&nbsp;we wdrożeniach&nbsp;<strong>Back Office</strong>.</li>\n<li>Minimum&nbsp;<strong>5 lat doświadczenia</strong>&nbsp;w raportowaniu i integracjach.</li>\n<li>Minimum&nbsp;<strong>4 lata doświadczenia</strong>&nbsp;z&nbsp;<strong>MxTest / Onyx</strong>.</li>\n<li>Znajomość j. angielskiego na poziomie min. B2.</li>\n<li>Bardzo dobra znajomość instrumentów:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Income</li>\n<li>Money Market</li>\n<li>Interest Rate Swap</li>\n<li>Cross Currency Swap</li>\n<li>FX Derivatives</li>\n</ul>\n<li>Doświadczenie w konfiguracji:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>BO module</li>\n<li>Reporting</li>\n<li>Onyx/MxTest</li>\n<li>Dynamic Tables, Simulation Views, Trade Query</li>\n<li>P&amp;L, Market Value, Risk Figures, One Stop Processing</li>\n<li>DataMart Reporting</li>\n</ul>\n',NULL,NULL),(1289,7805,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p><strong>To oferujemy:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Szansę na zdobycie doświadczenia w firmie będącej liderem na rynku rozwiązań FinTech,</li>\n<li>Kompleksowy program wdrożeniowy (onboarding),</li>\n<li>Doświadczony zespół z dużym know-how i bazą wiedzy dostępną dla każdego,</li>\n<li>Wewnętrzne szkolenia techniczne,<br></li>\n<li>Różne benefity.</li>\n</ul></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Wykształcenie wyższe (min. studia licencjackie) z zakresu informatyki, finansów i rachunkowości, metod ilościowych lub podobne,</li>\n<li>Znajomość języka SQL (MSSQL) min w zakresie prostych zapytań,</li>\n<li>Znajomość pakietu MS Office (w szczególności Word, Excel).</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1290,7806,'<h2 _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\"> Opis oferty </h2><common-posting-translate-section _ngcontent-serverapp-c2830789767=\"\" class=\"translate-section\" _nghost-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex align-items-center\"><inline-icon _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" maticon=\"g_translate\" class=\"mr-10 md-icon\" _nghost-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\"><svg _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" class=\"inline-svg\"><use _ngcontent-serverapp-c2305233609=\"\" href=\"#md-g_translate\"></use></svg></inline-icon><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"d-flex flex-wrap\"><span _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\"> Oryginalny tekst.&nbsp; </span><button _ngcontent-serverapp-c207996580=\"\" class=\"text-primary p-0 m-0\" data-cy=\"translate\"> Pokaż tłumaczenie </button></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></common-posting-translate-section><!----><nfj-read-more _ngcontent-serverapp-c2761484183=\"\" class=\"font-weight-normal\" _nghost-serverapp-c768264723=\"\"><div _ngcontent-serverapp-c768264723=\"\" class=\"tw-overflow-hidden\" style=\"line-height: 28px; height: auto;\"><p>We are&nbsp;monday.com, a global software company transforming how businesses run. Our product suite can adapt to the needs of diverse industries and use cases within one powerful platform, empowering ~250,000 customers worldwide to reimagine how work gets done, drive greater efficiency and scale like never before.</p>\n<p>With over 2,900 employees across the globe, we grow by prioritizing transparency and knowledge sharing. We care about the impact you make, not the hours you clock, so we encourage initiative, ownership, and fresh thinking. We back our people with flexible work, wellness and mental health support, and a work environment built on collaboration.</p>\n<p>We fully embrace the AI revolution and we equip you and our developers with AI-powered IDEs, customizable agent rules, prompt engineering tools to streamline your workflow and AI-infused CI/CD pipelines designed to boost speed and reliability. You\'ll also tap into AI-driven insights, helping you make smarter decisions, faster.<strong>We’re looking for a Senior Developer Experience Engineer (AI Tools / Agents / IDEs).</strong></p>\n<p>In this role, you’ll leverage your deep technical expertise and sound judgment to steer critical projects, provide architectural direction, and elevate the work of those around you. This track is ideal for engineers who excel at using their technical expertise to increase productivity and want to share it and inspire others.</p>\n<p>The role is based in our Warsaw office&nbsp;-&nbsp;established&nbsp;in 2022,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is a growing hub for engineers who love solving impactful problems. Teams here work on a broad range of challenges that push the boundaries of our products and infrastructure.</p>\n<p><strong>What&nbsp;</strong><strong>monday.com</strong><strong>&nbsp;can offer you:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>From Monday to Wednesday,&nbsp;we\'ll&nbsp;fuel your day with free breakfast and lunch in the office.</li>\n<li>Enjoy private medical care and Multisport card to keep you healthy.</li>\n<li>We\'ve got you covered with life insurance.</li>\n<li>We care of employee\'s mental health as well - you will get access to Calm Mindfulness App.</li>\n<li>Get awesome discounts on our partners\' products and services.</li>\n<li>Join in on our fun team events and get-togethers.</li>\n<li>Look forward to a little something special from us during your birthday and work anniversaries.</li>\n<li>For Online Learning opportunities, you will gain access to LinkedIn Learning.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p></div><!----><!----><!----></nfj-read-more><!---->','\n<li>Hands-on experience with&nbsp;<strong>AI/ML tooling</strong>&nbsp;and a solid understanding of the underlying technologies.</li>\n<li>Deep understanding of&nbsp;<strong>software engineering fundamentals</strong>, including architecture design, CI/CD, testing, observability, and performance optimization.</li>\n<li>Experience with&nbsp;<strong>modern IDEs</strong>&nbsp;(e.g., VS Code, JetBrains, Cursor).</li>\n<li>Strong&nbsp;<strong>programming expertise.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Exceptional communication</strong>&nbsp;and collaboration abilities, with experience working cross-functionally alongside engineers, product managers, and designers.</li>\n<li>A&nbsp;<strong>curious, growth-oriented mindset</strong>, with enthusiasm for exploring new technologies and continuously refining workflows.</li>\n<li>A genuine&nbsp;<strong>passion for developer experience</strong>, and for building tools that enhance engineering productivity and satisfaction.</li>\n',NULL,NULL),(1291,7807,'Enovation is an expert in eLearning solutions looking for an experienced Playwright Automation Tester . ','<li class=\"lxul5ps\">Nice to have: knowledge of Drupal, Moodle or Totara</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Working proficiency of the English language enabling written and verbal communication.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Minimum one year of work experience in a similar position.</li>',NULL,NULL),(1292,7808,'We work on projects that make vacationing easier and more pleasant. If you join us, you will get the opportunity to shape the experiences of users from all over the world. The varied pool of clients from all walks of life and presenting different online behaviors guarantees that working on our projects gives you a chance to constantly learn and develop in your field.','<li class=\"lxul5ps\">1+ year of experience with Boomi or a similar integration tool.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Solid backend development background.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Experience working with REST/SOAP APIs, XML, JSON, and data transformations.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Good understanding of integration concepts such as APIs, messaging queues, web services, event-driven architectures, and batch processing.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Familiarity with SQL and NoSQL databases.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Knowledge of cloud environments (AWS, Azure, GCP) and related integration capabilities.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Hands-on experience with Git or other version control systems.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Strong problem-solving and analytical skills, with attention to detail.</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Good English communication skills (spoken and written).</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Availability to work 2 days per week from the office in a hybrid setup.</li>',NULL,NULL),(1293,7809,'','<li class=\"lxul5ps\">Min. 3 lata doświadczenia w zarządzaniu projektami, zmianą lub analizie wymagań</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Wykształcenie wyższe – preferowane kierunki: ubezpieczenia, finanse, bankowość, ekonomia, kierunki ścisłe lub zarządzanie</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Umiejętność pracy z backlogiem, definiowania kryteriów akceptacji i oceny ryzyk</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Znajomość procesów taryfikacyjnych i analityki biznesowej</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Podstawowa wiedza z zakresu produktów ubezpieczeniowych</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Znajomość języka angielskiego na poziomie umożliwiającym pracę z dokumentacją i zespołami IT</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Znajomość metodyk zwinnych (Scrum, Agile)</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">Dodatkowym atutem będzie doświadczenie w prowadzeniu warsztatów i pracy z narzędziami analitycznymi</li>',NULL,NULL),(1294,7810,'OPis','<li class=\"lxul5ps\">wykształcenie wyższe,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">10 lat doświadczenia zawodowego, w tym 5 lat pracy na podobnym stanowisku,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">doświadczenie w projektach wdrożeniowych związanych z SAP,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">wiedza zawodowa w zakresie administracji, rachunkowości, podatków, IT,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">znajomość systemu SAP na zaawansowanym poziomie,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">znajomość języka angielskiego,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">umiejętność współpracy,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">umiejętność analitycznego myślenia,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">efektywność,</li><li class=\"lxul5ps\">samodzielność i dokładność.</li>',NULL,NULL),(1309,7827,'Cso','','','');
